  "title": "PROCUREMENT EXECUTIVE",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>JOB RESPONSIBILITES </strong></u></p><p>·        \nEnsure maintenance and compliance to ISO procedures and local\nstatutory requirement</p><p>·        \nPrepare purchase orders and liaise closely with suppliers to ensure\ntimely delivery</p><p>·        \nExecute expertise in cost comparisons to meet the Operations’\nrequirement with the interest of company in terms of quality and service</p><p>·        \nAssist to source for new competitive quotes from supplier</p><p>·        \nAssist to prepare monthly report for management</p><p>·        \nAny other ad-hoc duties as per assigned</p><p><u><strong>JOB REQUIREMENTS </strong></u></p><p>·       \nDiploma or Degree in Business Administration Preferred 3 Years relevant\nworking experience in a similar capacity preferably in Manufacturing Industry.</p><p>·       \nExcellent communications and negotiation skills with suppliers and\ninternal customers, ability to resolve issues </p><p>·       \nPossess analytical skills, able to justify purchases with figures </p><p>·       \nHardworking and meticulous with positive attitude </p><p>·       \nProficient in Microsoft Office Application (Words, Excel)</p><p>·       \nProcess good interpersonal, and coordination skill is crucial in this\nposition as main task will be executing festive season project </p><p>·       \nTeam Player with the ability to work independently with good organizing\nskills </p>",
